{{Infobox Journal | cover = <!-- Commented out because image was deleted: [[Image:ACHSC.png]] --> | discipline = [[Latin American studies]], [[History]], [[Technology]] | abbreviation = Anu. Colomb. Hist. Soc. Cult. | website = http://www.humanas.unal.edu.co/achsc/RegistroRevista.php | publisher = [[Universidad Nacional de Colombia]] | country = [[Colombia]] | history = 1963–present | ISSN = 0120-2456 }}
The '''''Anuario Colombiano de Historia Social y de la Cultura''''' is an [[academic journal]] founded in 1963 by Jaime Jaramillo Uribe. It is published by the history departament of [[National University of Colombia]]. It has been recognized as the main publication of Colombian historical studies{{Citation needed|date=December 2007}}. Authors are national and international scholars.
The journal is published annually.
